 per page (Pages) or per scroll chunk (Lazy / Auto-advance).\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./src/renderer/src/i18n/en.ts","start":11280,"length":93,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'resultsPageSize' which is declared here on type '{ readonly keySaved: \"Key saved\"; readonly loraPath: \"LoRA → {lora} · Checkpoint → {checkpoint}\"; readonly outputFolders: \"Downloads go directly into these folders by model type. Routing tag (e.g. Krea2) adds a subfolder — LoRA → …\\\\Lora\\\\Krea2, Checkpoint → …\\\\Checkpoints\\\\Krea2. Tag Folders can override with a cus...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":11768,"length":19,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"Tas pats kaip 👁 mygtukas šalia Blur antraštėje. Off = išvalo Browse korteles ir tylesnis UI (atsisiuntimai vis tiek vyksta); On = gyvas Browse tinklelis.\"' is not assignable to type '\"Same as the 👁 button next to Blur in the header. Off = clear Browse cards and quieter UI (downloads still run); On = live Browse grid.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./src/renderer/src/i18n/en.ts","start":11382,"length":167,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'updateBrowseOnCrawl' which is declared here on type '{ readonly keySaved: \"Key saved\"; readonly loraPath: \"LoRA → {lora} · Checkpoint → {checkpoint}\"; readonly outputFolders: \"Downloads go directly into these folders by model type. Routing tag (e.g. Krea2) adds a subfolder — LoRA → …\\\\Lora\\\\Krea2, Checkpoint → …\\\\Checkpoints\\\\Krea2. Tag Folders can override with a cus...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":11963,"length":6,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"civitai.red = pilnas katalogas (SFW+NSFW) vienu API. civitai.com = SFW orientuotas hostas. Brandą ribokite Browse taisyklės filteriu — dvigubas crawl nebereikalingas.\"' is not assignable to type '\"civitai.red = full catalog (SFW+NSFW) via one API. civitai.com = SFW-oriented host. Filter maturity per Browse rule — dual crawl is obsolete.\"'.